  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or ALICANTE - charts 19-1, 19-2 and 19-3 from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017. <br>You are approaching Alicante from the southwest to follow the south route. Which path should be followed in case of a radio communication failure?</p>",
